==English==

===Noun===
'''guaranty'''

# {{law}} An [[undertaking]] to answer for the [[payment]] of some [[debt]], or the [[performance]] of some [[contract]] or [[duty]], of another, in case of the [[failure]] of such other to pay or [[perform]]; a [[guarantee]]; a [[warranty]]; a [[security]].
# Something serving as a [[security]] for such an [[undertaking]].

